data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT ALERT! Your dream home just got more affordable!! And if you get pre-approved with our preferred lender we'll sprinkle an extra $1000 lender closing cost credit on top. With the recent price improvement, this opportunity is simply too spectacular to pass up! You have just discovered a hidden gem nestled in the heart of the 2-square-mile community in Mt. Greenwood, home to many of Chicago's first responders. This beautifully renovated all-brick Cape Cod home sits prominently in the center of it all, boasting an unheard of 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, ensuring ample personal space for everyone!    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by sophisticated wainscoting and hardwood floors that run throughout. The kitchen, outfitted with stainless steel appliances, sleek grey soft-close cabinets and drawers, a spacious farm sink, and custom countertops, seamlessly connects to the dining room, making meal prep and family dinners a breeze. The main level offers easy access to the deck, large, fenced backyard, and a recently built 2-car garage provides plenty of parking and storage. The owner's suite serves as a luxurious haven for unwinding, featuring an indulgent shower equipped with built-in seating, full-body spray panels, invigorating wall jets, and a soothing waterfall setting.    Downstairs, you'll find a fully finished lower level with walk out access, a private bedroom, luxurious bathroom, and two spacious recreation rooms. It's perfect for a teenage hangout, cozy home theater or an engaging area for the whole family to enjoy.     You'll enjoy convenient transportation options and shopping choices while relishing the peace of this hidden oasis. This home is within walking distance of the renowned Mt. Greenwood elementary school, Mount Greenwood Park, and the Chicago High School for Agricultural Sciences. Offering you the amenities, comfort, and sense of community you've been longing for. Welcome home! You are going to love it here!
